    <div class="card hero">
      <h1>Assistant Hub</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome! This site combines multiple mini tools to help you manage money, plan investing,
        grow your career, prepare for interviews, and stay organised with tasks.
      </p>

      <div class="quick-actions">
        <a class="btn" href="/task-management">Open Task Management</a>
